body:
### Description

Error:
```
1) App\Test\TestCase\Controller\AuthControllerTest::test_forgot_password
Possibly related to League\Container\Exception\NotFoundException: 
"Unable to extend alias (App\Service\User\ForgotPassword) as it is not being managed as a definition" 
#0 /srv/app/vendor/cakephp/cakephp/src/Core/TestSuite/ContainerStubTrait.php(147): League\Container\Container->extend('App\\Service\\Use...')

```

Container Code:
```php
# in src/Application.php
    public function services(ContainerInterface $container): void
    {
        $container->add(ComponentRegistry::class);
        $container->delegate(new ReflectionContainer());
    }
```

Controller:
```php
    public function forgotPassword(ForgotPassword $forgotPassword)
    {
        if ($this->request->is('post')) {
            $this->Flash->info(__('A password reset has been sent. If you do not receive an email please contact support'));
            $forgotPassword->reset($this->request->getData('email'));
            $this->redirect('/login');
        }
    }
```

Test Case:
```php
# in a TestCase class
    public function test_forgot_password(): void
    {
        $user = UserFactory::make(['last_login' => FrozenTime::parse()])->persist();
        $this->mockService(ForgotPassword::class, function() {
            $mail = $this->createPartialMock(MailgunSender::class, [
               'send'
            ]);
            $mail->expects($this->once())->method('send')->willReturn(SendResponse::create([]));
            /** @var $usersTable UsersTable */
            $usersTable = $this->getTableLocator()->get('Users');
            return new ForgotPassword($usersTable, $mail);
        });

        $this->post(self::FORGOT_PASSWORD_URL, [
            'email' => $user->get('email'),
        ]);

        $this->assertRedirect(self::USER_LOGIN_URL);
    }
```

If I explicitly add the following the test passes:
```php
# in src/Application.php
    public function services(ContainerInterface $container): void
    {
        $container->add(ComponentRegistry::class);
        $container->add(ForgotPassword::class);
        $container->delegate(new ReflectionContainer());
    }
```

### CakePHP Version

4.4.4

### PHP Version

8.0
